to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"major athletes\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just down to help those in need who are representing all of us.\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"need\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the type of awareness I have been trying to bring to these Olympians,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the type\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3069}, {\"ngram\": \"awareness\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3082}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympians\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Independenthas contacted representatives for Flavor Flav and Ohanian for comment.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3191, \"end\": 3202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3086708562464574e-33, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Independenthas\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3160}, {\"ngram\": \"representatives\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3186}, {\"ngram\": \"Ohanian\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3214}, {\"ngram\": \"comment\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flavor Flav has continued to be vocal about advocating for fellow Olympians.\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3305, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3240}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow Olympians\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, two months before he officially announced his sponsorship with the US Water Polo teams, he'd already shared his plans to work with them on social media.\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3